<div class="container">
  <h1>Edit Your Profile</h1>
  <h4>Your <b>username</b> is the name you used to sign on. <br> Your <b>handle</b> is the name that other CityHackers will see. <br> Your <b>email</b> will only be revealed to other CityHackers if you both agree to be friends.<br> Your <b>interests</b> are 1-3 activities that you love to do. <br> Your <b>bio</b> describes those interests.<br> Your <b>Friendships</b> tab lists all of the CityHackers you can meet up with!
  <h/4>
  <hr>
  <div class="well">
    <div class="row">
      <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
        <li class="active"><a href="#home" data-toggle="tab">Profile</a></li>
        <li><a href="#profile" data-toggle="tab">Friendships</a></li>
      </ul>
      <hr>
      <div id="myTabContent" class="tab-content">
        <div class="tab-pane active in" id="home">
          {{partial "profile-tab"}}
        </div>

        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="profile">
          {{partial "profile-friendship-tab"}}
        </div>
      </div>{{!-- tab-content --}}
    </div>{{!-- row --}}
  </div>{{!-- well --}}
</div>{{!-- container --}}
<hr>
